类 HeapStackFrame

org.overrun.swgl.core.io.HeapStackFrame

AutoCloseable
@Deprecated(since="0.2.0") public class HeapStackFrame extends Object implements AutoCloseable
已过时。
Use memAlloc or memCalloc to avoid constructing objects.
The heap in auto-closeable.

Example

try (var heap = new HeapStackFrame()) {
     var bb = heap.utilMemAlloc(8196).put(bytes).flip();
     ProcessBuffer(bb);
 }
